{"tid":1066332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵荃灣線下半年轉用新信號系統　預告初期會有「陣痛」較多故障","createTime":"2019-03-18T00:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T02:42:27.000Z","uid":37554,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d053224fc5e62bc2d107d9f4a6a980f03dd89cdb","tid":1066332,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:22:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵今年下半年會在荃灣線轉用新信號系統，初期會以「雙系統」營運，即新舊系統一同使用。港鐵預告，轉用新系統初期會有「陣痛」，故障率或較高，會做好應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成表示，港鐵會逐一將列車轉為新系統，一旦發生故障，會停用相關列車。他說，按照經驗，轉用新系統初期會有較多故障，港鐵會做好應變措施，包括一旦出現服務延誤，會提供接駁巴士，及透過App向乘客廣播。<br />\n<br />\n此外，港鐵去年準點率為99.9%，全年有12宗延誤31分鐘或以上的事故，包括去年10月發生的四線故障（計算為4宗事故），罰款金額約2000萬元"},{"pid":"f1145684267409b4363ae15b87bd00950a61c16e","tid":1066332,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係要撞多幾次？"},{"pid":"bfabab1b5a3dd71145e8e6e1d1982aede48a6f32","tid":1066332,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1145684267409b4363ae15b87bd00950a61c16e","tid":1066332,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係要撞多幾次？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:27:36.000Z","msg":"又要加價"},{"pid":"ebac3362209f628a90c7e373e36859ebc1af95dd","tid":1066332,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f1145684267409b4363ae15b87bd00950a61c16e","tid":1066332,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係要撞多幾次？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:27:37.000Z","msg":"陣痛！"},{"pid":"3f198710425ef79fce3a2349e4f1a4ecddd7120e","tid":1066332,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfabab1b5a3dd71145e8e6e1d1982aede48a6f32","tid":1066332,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1145684267409b4363ae15b87bd00950a61c16e","tid":1066332,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"咁即係要撞多幾次？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:27:36.000Z","msg":"又要加價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:28:10.000Z","msg":"幫佢比維修費"},{"pid":"896855628772a0c4e0fa026023eda0072196112f","tid":1066332,"uid":36178,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:29:05.000Z","msg":"撞到marvel系列咁都叫「陣痛」"},{"pid":"e750a4c14cb16f85b38c737b1f242a6e76c44198","tid":1066332,"uid":197219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:29:22.000Z","msg":"比條reference呀大佬，你話乜就乜咩"},{"pid":"e7d662839346aa98a9fa7de5c34502549948ba16","tid":1066332,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"陣痛都撞車點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0afe9509699669d410c9c8035d3a63d65d0d566","tid":1066332,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"[url]陣痛都只不過係inception[/url]"},{"pid":"e66c91681d259c54cd3f0abb807c837f7a70ff8b","tid":1066332,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"港鐵:我一早賣左廣告,提左市民訊號系統會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1011ba822b58360037bf6014892e7155bf026ca","tid":1066332,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"896855628772a0c4e0fa026023eda0072196112f","tid":1066332,"uid":36178,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:29:05.000Z","msg":"撞到marvel系列咁都叫「陣痛」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"人地話陣痛就陣痛啦   駁咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a4a7b6c5278c563f4d85c598eec5caca6588e0","tid":1066332,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"非營業時間，唔算係延誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif